　　About　　Became known for her roles in such made-for-TV movies as If I Had Wings and The Unauthorized Saved By the Bell Story. In 2018, she began starring as Judy Robinson in Netflix's Lost in Space.　　Before Fame　　She began her professional acting career and launched a Twitter account in early 2012.　　Trivia　　She acted with Brittney Wilson, Bradley Steven Perry, and Tyrel Jackson Williams in a 2014 television movie called Pants On Fire.　　Family Life　　She grew up in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, and has also gone by the name of Taylor Russell McKenzie.　　Associated With　　Early in her career, she appeared with Madeline Carroll in a CBS TV movie titled Blink.
